Subject: [PATCH] vdpa: Enable a user to add and delete a vdpa device
Git-commit: 903f7bcaedb84ca47998e609015a34ddde93742e
Patch-mainline: v5.12-rc2
References: bsn#12
Modified-by-SEL: No


Add the ability to add and delete a vdpa device.

Examples:
Create a vdpa device of type network named "foo2" from
the management device vdpasim:

$ vdpa dev add mgmtdev vdpasim_net name foo2

Delete the vdpa device after its use:
$ vdpa dev del foo2

